synopsis: "Hardcaml EDA Tools Config"
description: """
Library for configuring paths to external EDA tool paths used by Hardcaml libraries. This
can be used to configure Hardcaml to use your local environment setup by pinning a custom
(local-install) version of this library. Defaults to relying on tools available in PATH.
"""
